bhop lethargic

around a minute long
factoryish theme - loosely based off of skaebne
three bonuses around 10-20s each

bhop is dead. Didn't do any external testing besides myself. hopefully there isn't anything map breaking or gross, but I did go through it quite a bit myself. I think the map is fun personally, and there are a couple of optional routes scattered throughout the map. I attempted to balance them but we will see if that worked. Enjoy!

let me know if there are any issues.

edit: made the map in a day and a half. map name is indicative to how I feel about life atm
